Package cz.fel.cvut.openk8s.migration.service.migration

Interface MigrationProvider

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ConfigMapMigrationProvider, DeploymentMigrationProvider, PodMigrationProvider, ReplicaSetMigrationProvider, SecretsMigrationProvider, ServiceAccountMigrationProvider, ServiceMigrationProvider
    public interface MigrationProvider
    This interface should be implemented if you want to extend Kubernetes items list, for that migration is supported.

                                                        java.util.function.Consumer<io.fabric8.kubernetes.api.model.HasMetadata> callback)
        Migrates list of items from Kubernetes to OpenShift cluster
        Parameters:
        items - items to migrate
        kubernetesClient - -kubernetes client, connected to the cluster
        openShiftClient - openShift client, connected to the cluster
        callback - action, that will be done after item was migrated
        Returns:

        Throws:
